(Worked Examples) Tj
T*
(Worked Example 1) Tj
T*
(1. Start with an example based on reducing a passage into a few clear sentences.) Tj
T*
(2. Identify the exact idea in main ideas, concise expression, and omission of repetition) Tj
T*
(that the question is testing.) Tj
T*
(3. Apply the correct method for Summary step by step without skipping reasoning.) Tj
T*
(4. Check the final answer and explain why it is correct.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Worked Example 2) Tj
T*
(1. Choose a second example that still focuses on shortening passages into key points.) Tj
T*
(2. Break the task into smaller parts and link each part to the rule being used.) Tj
T*
(3. Point out how to avoid copying large parts of the original text while solving it.) Tj
T*
(4. Review the result and connect it back to the topic overview.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
